* text=auto eol=lf
*.pkl binary
*.joblib binary
*.mp4 binary
*.json -text

# Append-only changelog: every PR prepends a new block at the top, so any two
# concurrent PRs collide on the exact same first hunk when the merge-train daemon
# rebases them serially (T-2026-CU-9050-142). The built-in union merge driver
# keeps BOTH sides on conflict instead of aborting the rebase — so parallel
# changelog appends auto-resolve and the train stops stalling on CHANGELOG.md.
# Ordering of two simultaneous entries is not guaranteed (cosmetic); both survive.
# Deliberately NOT applied to AUDIT_TODO.md: its edits are checkbox toggles on
# existing lines, where union would wrongly keep both the checked and unchecked
# variant.
CHANGELOG.md merge=union
